B.aaJ=new A.c1("A 60-year-old patient presents with progressive back pain and bilateral leg weakness. What is the most likely etiology?",B.Yy,1,"In older patients, spinal stenosis due to degenerative changes is the leading cause, often presenting with bilateral symptoms.")
B.a1z=s(["0-5%","10-30%","50-70%","90-100%"],t.s)
